videos.description: No one boxes out Blake Griffin who rushes into the paint and leaps to grab the missed shot for an emphatic putback slam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Griffin skies for putback slam) 2021/06/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin skies for putback slam

videos.description: Kyrie Irving uses an in-and-out move to shake his defender for a layup, but Giannis Antetokounmpo flies in for an amazing block out of nowhere and Brook Lopez follows up with a 3.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis shuts down Kyrie's highlight move, Lopez drains 3) 2021/06/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis shuts down Kyrie's highlight move, Lopez drains 3

videos.description: Blake Griffin gets the pass and elevates on the baseline to hammer down a dunk in the face of Giannis Antetokounmpo with authority.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Blake throws down on Giannis) 2021/06/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Blake throws down on Giannis

videos.description: Kevin Durant is in his bag as he crosses over Giannis Antetokounmpo multiple times before he pulls up to sink an and-1 jumper in his face.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD crosses up Giannis for and-1 bucket) 2021/06/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD crosses up Giannis for and-1 bucket

videos.description: Kevin Durant blows by Giannis Antetokounmpo and gets to the rack to make an amazing reverse layup in the final moments of the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD burns Giannis for sweet reverse to end the 3rd) 2021/06/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD burns Giannis for sweet reverse to end the 3rd

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo describes his even-keeled demeanor and says he still believes in the Bucks despite their dropping two games in a row to the Nets.
